      "detail": "Supervision levels for UK AI deployments follow the same commercial standards as other markets. No UK-specific regulation mandates tighter supervision for AI systems. Human-on-loop autonomy is a product-design choice rather than a jurisdiction-specific requirement. The training constraint does not affect operational autonomy at the deployment level."
    },
